import React from 'react';
import { Navbar,Badge, Nav, NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap';

const Navigation = () => (
  <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" bg="white">
    <Navbar.Brand className ="text-primary" href="#home">LOGO BRAND</Navbar.Brand>
    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
    <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
      <Nav className="mr-auto" />
      <Nav>
        <Nav.Link className="mr-3" href="#deets">Products</Nav.Link>
        <Nav.Link className="mr-3" href="#memes">
          Account
        </Nav.Link>
        <Nav.Link className="mr-3" href="#memes">
          Checkout
        </Nav.Link>
        <Nav.Link className="mr-3" href="#memes">
          Cart
          <Badge variant="black">9</Badge>
        </Nav.Link>
        <NavDropdown title="Thuong Le" id="collasible-nav-dropdown">
          <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Account</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Your Shop</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">Something</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Divider />
          <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">Log Out</NavDropdown.Item>
        </NavDropdown>
      </Nav>
    </Navbar.Collapse>
  </Navbar>
);

export default Navigation;
